data.description: This home is well appointed for anyone who prefers hardwoods and ceramic tile in the main areas of the home.  The only location of carpet is on the stairs to the second floor.  The kitchen features gas appliances for cooking, a must for those who really like to cook.  The backyard entertaining is enhanced with a full-length covered patio.  4 bedrooms with 2 and one-half baths allow plenty of room for the new resident. There are plenty of mature trees for those hot summer days spent enjoying family time outside.
